            <div style="flex-shrink: 0;">
                <canvas id="ratingsChart" width="600" height="300"></canvas>
            </div>
            <div style="max-width: 300px; text-align: left;">
                <p>
                    Castle Climbers has received overwhelmingly positive reviews, with the majority of players
                    rating it 5 stars for its fun gameplay, smooth controls, and challenging level design.
                    The intuitive mechanics and replay value have made it a favorite among platformer fans.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


    <section class="description">
        <h4>Game Stats</h4>
