                <p>189,839m</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h5>Total Coins</h5>
                <p>145,522</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h5>Total Points</h5>
                <p>693,460</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h5>Total Time Played</h5>
                <p>88h 20m</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="description">
        <h4>What I Learned</h4>
        <p>
            This project taught me about player feedback loops, camera smoothing, and efficient sprite animation.
            It also gave me experience fine-tuning difficulty curves and level pacing.
        </p>
    </section>
}
